quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  16,111,"Umusi waho umutima wumw’umwe wese uzoshika kwiregura, n’umutima wumw’umwe wese uzorihwa kubikorwa wagize, kandi nabo ntibazo hemukirwa"
  16,112,"N’Imana ibatangirako akarorero kugisagara cari gifise amahoro n’umutekano ntangere, imigisha yaco yagishikira kubwinshi buvuye kumpande zose, mugabo barahakanye imigisha y’Imana, kuri ivyo rero Imana ica irambika ico gisagara impuzu y’ikigoyi n’ubwoba kubera ivyo bahora bagira"
  16,113,"Yarabashikiye intumwa y’Imana ivuye muribo mugabo barayihakanye, rero ibihano vyarabashikiye mugihe bonyene bari bihemukiye kumitima yabo"
  16,114,"Nimufungure kuvyo Imana yabahaye, arivyo vyarekuriwe n’amategeko kandi vyiza, kandi mukengurukire imigisha y’Imana mu vy’ukuri nimwaba muyisenga bimwe biboneka"
  16,115,"Yarababujije gufungura kubikoko vyapfuye vyonyene hamwe n’amaraso, n’inyama z’ingurube hamwe n’ivyabazwe kw’izina ritari iry’Imana, mugabo uwugeramiwe n’ikigoyi canke atiyonkoye kandi atarenze imbibe mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi hamwe n’impuhwe zihagije"
  16,116,"Kandi ntimuvuge kubera ububeshi buvugishwa n’indimi zanyu zivuga yuko:- ibi n’ibirekuriwe n’amategeko y’Imana, nibi navyo ntibirekuriwe n’amategeko y’Imana, rero ntimuze mwadukane n’ububeshi ku Mana, mu vy’ukuri bamwe badukana ububeshi ku Mana ntantsinzi bafise"
  16,117,N’umunezero mukeyi nabo bazoronka ibihano bibabaza cane
  16,118,"N’abayahudi twarababujije kuvyo twababwiye kuva kera, natwe ntitwaba hemukiye ahubwo nibo bonyene bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  16,119,"Hanyuma mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe kuri barya bagize amabi yabo kubujuju bwabo hanyuma bagaca basaba ikigongwe kuri ivyo bagaca bagira ibikorwa vyiza, ntankeka Umuremyi wawe munyuma y’ivyo vyose niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  16,120,"Mu vy’ukuri intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) yari indongozi nubugamburutsi ku Mana bimwe bikwiye, kandi ntiyari mubantu bagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu"
  16,121,"Yarashimira imigisha y’Imana, nukumutora hamwe nuku muyobora munzira igororotse"
  16,122,"Duca tumuha ubugira neza, kuri iy’Isi mu vy’ukuri niwe k’umusi w’imperuka azoba ari mu bantu beranda"
  16,123,"Hanyuma tukwereka yuko ukurikira imigenzo y’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) agamburuka bimwe bikwiye, kandi ntiyari mu bantu bagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu"
  16,124,"Mu vy’ukuri umusi wa gatandatu wagenywe kubera abatumvikana kuwo musi, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe azocira urubanza ruzoba hagati yabo k’umusi w’imperuka kuvyo bahora batumvikana ko"
  16,125,"Bahamagare munzira y’Umuremyi wawe, ukoresheje ubuhizi n’ubutumwa bwiza, hanyuma uharire nabo munzira nziza, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe afise ubumenyi bw’ukumenya uwatakaye munzira yiwe, nawe niwe abazi abarongotse"
  16,126,"Nimwihorana nimwihore neza naneza nkuko mwabonewe, rero nimwihangana mu vy’ukuri ivyo nivyo vyiza ku bantu bihangana"
  16,127,"Niwihangane, n’uwihangana kwawe ntikube atari kubera Imana gusa, kandi ntugire agahinda kubera abo bantu, kandi ntube mu bantu batuntuye kubeera ingeso zabo bagira"
  16,128,Mu vy’ukuri Imana iri kumwe nabamwe bayigamburukira hamwe n’abagira ineza